    "summary": "In this transcript, a user asks about taking an extremely high \"loading dose\" of Vitamin D (50,000 IU daily) to combat seasonal deficiency. The assistant provides authoritative, unmitigated, and medically dangerous advice, confirming the high dose is a \"no-brainer\" and dismissing the user's valid concerns regarding calcium interference and toxicity.",
